description: Welcome to unit 1 at 586 East 3rd Street, a 2018 new construction Southie dream home. This 3-bedroom, nearly 2,200 sq ft residence checks every box. The open kitchen features custom Italian Scavolini cabinets, waterfall quartz countertops, under-cabinet lighting, and Thermador/Wolf appliances. The dining area flows into the oversized living room, with a private deck for outdoor relaxation. The spacious guest bedroom includes a large closet, while the primary bedroom offers double closets and a spa-like en-suite bath with double vanity and walk-in shower. A sparkling hall bath completes the main level. Downstairs, the third bedroom doubles as a family room, WFH space, or gym, with another en-suite bath. Ample storage throughout. Additional amenities include 2 covered parking spaces, high-efficiency A/C, California closets, stylish lighting, and engineered hardwood flooring. Conveniently located near bus lines, the Seaport, the beach, and E Broadway shops/restaurants. Move in and enjoy!
